## Configuration and Dependencies

10. Avoid hardcoding values. Use constructor arguments, config objects, or environment variables.

11. Declare dependencies in `pyproject.toml`:

```toml
[project]
name = "my-sdk"
version = "0.1.0"
dependencies = ["requests", "pydantic"]
```

12. Optional dependencies can be installed via extras:

```bash
pip install my-sdk[playwright]
```

